As a professional paper, it boasts rich, sharp color that won't fade or yellow, creating beautiful prints that will last for years to come. All prints are available in the following sizes... 8 x 10, 16 x 20, 20 x 24, 24 x 36. Select pieces are offered in a square format where possible, cropped directly in the center of the image. If curious about framing options, panel prints, printing on canvas, etc... don't hesitate to email me and we can work something out. Shipments take place within 24 hours of ordering.
